CREATE TABLE [umbracoUser] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[userDisabled] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_userDisabled] DEFAULT ('0'),
[userNoConsole] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_userNoConsole] DEFAULT ('0'),
[userName] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[userLogin] NVARCHAR(125) NOT NULL,
[userPassword] NVARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
[passwordConfig] NVARCHAR(500) NULL,
[userEmail] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[userLanguage] NVARCHAR(10) NULL,
[securityStampToken] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[failedLoginAttempts] INTEGER NULL,
[lastLockoutDate] DATETIME NULL,
[lastPasswordChangeDate] DATETIME NULL,
[lastLoginDate] DATETIME NULL,
[emailConfirmedDate] DATETIME NULL,
[invitedDate] DATETIME NULL,
[createDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_createDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[updateDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoUser_updateDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[avatar] NVARCHAR(500) NULL,
[tourData] NTEXT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoUser] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_user] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoUser_userLogin] ON [umbracoUser] ([userLogin])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoNode] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1060,1),
[uniqueId] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoNode_uniqueId] DEFAULT (NEWID()),
[parentId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[level] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[path] NVARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
[sortOrder] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[trashed] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoNode_trashed] DEFAULT ('0'),
[nodeUser] INTEGER NULL,
[text] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[nodeObjectType] UniqueIdentifier NULL,
[createDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoNode_createDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()))
ALTER TABLE [umbracoNode] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoNode] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_UniqueId] ON [umbracoNode] ([uniqueId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_ParentId] ON [umbracoNode] ([parentId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_Path] ON [umbracoNode] ([path])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_Trashed] ON [umbracoNode] ([trashed])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoNode_ObjectType] ON [umbracoNode] ([nodeObjectType])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoNode] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoNode_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([parentId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoNode] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoNode_umbracoUser_id] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeUser]) REFERENCES [umbracoUser] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [cmsContentType] ([pk] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(535,1),
[nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[alias] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[icon] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[thumbnail] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsContentType_thumbnail] DEFAULT ('folder.png'),
[description] NVARCHAR(1500) NULL,
[isContainer] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsContentType_isContainer] DEFAULT ('0'),
[isElement] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsContentType_isElement] DEFAULT ('0'),
[allowAtRoot] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsContentType_allowAtRoot] DEFAULT ('0'),
[variations] INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsContentType_variations] DEFAULT ('1'))
ALTER TABLE [cmsContentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsContentType] PRIMARY KEY ([pk])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsContentType] ON [cmsContentType] ([nodeId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsContentType_icon] ON [cmsContentType] ([icon])
ALTER TABLE [cmsContentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsContentType_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [cmsTemplate] ([pk] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[alias] NVARCHAR(100) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [cmsTemplate] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsTemplate] PRIMARY KEY ([pk])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsTemplate_nodeId] ON [cmsTemplate] ([nodeId])
ALTER TABLE [cmsTemplate] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsTemplate_umbracoNode] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoContent] ([nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[contentTypeId] INTEGER NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContent] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoContent] PRIMARY KEY ([nodeId])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContent] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoContent_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContent] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoContent_cmsContentType_NodeId] FOREIGN KEY ([contentTypeId]) REFERENCES [cmsContentType] ([NodeId])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoContentVersion] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[versionDate] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoContentVersion_versionDate] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[userId] INTEGER NULL,
[current] BIT NOT NULL,
[text] NVARCHAR(255) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContentVersion] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoContentVersion] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoContentVersion_NodeId] ON [umbracoContentVersion] ([nodeId],[current])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContentVersion] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoContentVersion_umbracoContent_nodeId] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoContent] ([nodeId])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoContentVersion] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoContentVersion_umbracoUser_id] FOREIGN KEY ([userId]) REFERENCES [umbracoUser] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoMediaVersion] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[path] NVARCHAR(255) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoMediaVersion] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoMediaVersion] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoMediaVersion] ON [umbracoMediaVersion] ([id],[path])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoMediaVersion] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoMediaVersion_umbracoContentVersion_id] FOREIGN KEY ([id]) REFERENCES [umbracoContentVersion] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoDocument] ([nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[published] BIT NOT NULL,
[edited] BIT NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoDocument] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoDocument] PRIMARY KEY ([nodeId])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoDocument_Published] ON [umbracoDocument] ([published])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoDocument] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoDocument_umbracoContent_nodeId] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoContent] ([nodeId])

CREATE TABLE [cmsDocumentType] ([contentTypeNodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[templateNodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[IsDefault] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsDocumentType_IsDefault] DEFAULT ('0'))
ALTER TABLE [cmsDocumentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsDocumentType] PRIMARY KEY ([contentTypeNodeId], [templateNodeId])
ALTER TABLE [cmsDocumentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsDocumentType_cmsContentType_nodeId] FOREIGN KEY ([contentTypeNodeId]) REFERENCES [cmsContentType] ([nodeId])
ALTER TABLE [cmsDocumentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsDocumentType_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([contentTypeNodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])
ALTER TABLE [cmsDocumentType] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsDocumentType_cmsTemplate_nodeId] FOREIGN KEY ([templateNodeId]) REFERENCES [cmsTemplate] ([nodeId])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoDataType] ([nodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[propertyEditorAlias] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[dbType] NVARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
[config] NTEXT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoDataType] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoDataType] PRIMARY KEY ([nodeId])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoDataType] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoDataType_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([nodeId]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [cmsDictionary] ([pk] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[id] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL,
[parent] UniqueIdentifier NULL,
[key] NVARCHAR(450) NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [cmsDictionary] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsDictionary] PRIMARY KEY ([pk])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsDictionary_id] ON [cmsDictionary] ([id])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsDictionary_Parent] ON [cmsDictionary] ([parent])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsDictionary_key] ON [cmsDictionary] ([key])
ALTER TABLE [cmsDictionary] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsDictionary_cmsDictionary_id] FOREIGN KEY ([parent]) REFERENCES [cmsDictionary] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoLanguage] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(2,1),
[languageISOCode] NVARCHAR(14) NULL,
[languageCultureName] NVARCHAR(100) NULL,
[isDefaultVariantLang] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoLanguage_isDefaultVariantLang] DEFAULT ('0'),
[mandatory] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoLanguage_mandatory] DEFAULT ('0'),
[fallbackLanguageId] INTEGER NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoLanguage] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoLanguage] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoLanguage_languageISOCode] ON [umbracoLanguage] ([languageISOCode])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoLanguage_fallbackLanguageId] ON [umbracoLanguage] ([fallbackLanguageId])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoLanguage] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoLanguage_umbracoLanguage_id] FOREIGN KEY ([fallbackLanguageId]) REFERENCES [umbracoLanguage] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [cmsLanguageText] ([pk] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[languageId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[UniqueId] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL,
[value] NVARCHAR(1000) NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [cmsLanguageText] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsLanguageText] PRIMARY KEY ([pk])
ALTER TABLE [cmsLanguageText] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsLanguageText_umbracoLanguage_id] FOREIGN KEY ([languageId]) REFERENCES [umbracoLanguage] ([id])
ALTER TABLE [cmsLanguageText] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsLanguageText_cmsDictionary_id] FOREIGN KEY ([UniqueId]) REFERENCES [cmsDictionary] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoDomain] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[domainDefaultLanguage] INTEGER NULL,
[domainRootStructureID] INTEGER NULL,
[domainName] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoDomain] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoDomain] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoDomain] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoDomain_umbracoNode_id] FOREIGN KEY ([domainRootStructureID]) REFERENCES [umbracoNode] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [umbracoLog] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[userId] INTEGER NULL,
[NodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[entityType] NVARCHAR(50) NULL,
[Datestamp] DATETIME NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_umbracoLog_Datestamp] DEFAULT (GETDATE()),
[logHeader] NVARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
[logComment] NVARCHAR(4000) NULL,
[parameters] NVARCHAR(500) NULL)
ALTER TABLE [umbracoLog] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_umbracoLog] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_umbracoLog] ON [umbracoLog] ([NodeId])
ALTER TABLE [umbracoLog] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_umbracoLog_umbracoUser_id] FOREIGN KEY ([userId]) REFERENCES [umbracoUser] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [cmsMacro] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[uniqueId] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL,
[macroUseInEditor] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMacro_macroUseInEditor] DEFAULT ('0'),
[macroRefreshRate] INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMacro_macroRefreshRate] DEFAULT ('0'),
[macroAlias] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[macroName] NVARCHAR(255) NULL,
[macroCacheByPage] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMacro_macroCacheByPage] DEFAULT ('1'),
[macroCachePersonalized] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMacro_macroCachePersonalized] DEFAULT ('0'),
[macroDontRender] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMacro_macroDontRender] DEFAULT ('0'),
[macroSource] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[macroType] INTEGER NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [cmsMacro] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsMacro] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsMacro_UniqueId] ON [cmsMacro] ([uniqueId])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsMacroPropertyAlias] ON [cmsMacro] ([macroAlias])

CREATE TABLE [cmsMacroProperty] ([id] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[uniquePropertyId] UniqueIdentifier NOT NULL,
[editorAlias] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
[macro] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[macroPropertySortOrder] INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMacroProperty_macroPropertySortOrder] DEFAULT ('0'),
[macroPropertyAlias] NVARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
[macroPropertyName] NVARCHAR(255) NOT NULL)
ALTER TABLE [cmsMacroProperty] ADD CONSTRAINT [PK_cmsMacroProperty] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsMacroProperty_UniquePropertyId] ON [cmsMacroProperty] ([uniquePropertyId])
CREATE UNIQUE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_cmsMacroProperty_Alias] ON [cmsMacroProperty] ([macro],[macroPropertyAlias])
ALTER TABLE [cmsMacroProperty] ADD CONSTRAINT [FK_cmsMacroProperty_cmsMacro_id] FOREIGN KEY ([macro]) REFERENCES [cmsMacro] ([id])

CREATE TABLE [cmsMemberType] ([pk] INTEGER NOT NULL IDENTITY(1,1),
[NodeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[propertytypeId] INTEGER NOT NULL,
[memberCanEdit] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMemberType_memberCanEdit] DEFAULT ('0'),
[viewOnProfile] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMemberType_viewOnProfile] DEFAULT ('0'),
[isSensitive] BIT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_cmsMemberType_isSensitive] DEFAULT ('0'))
